### Test Lecturer Classes API

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8386
@lecturerId = 22bfd357-e85d-40a7-8670-5bb5d545af83

### 1. Get all classes for lecturer (without filters)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/lecturer/classes
X-User-Id: {{lecturerId}}

### 2. Get all classes with pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/lecturer/classes?page=0&size=10
X-User-Id: {{lecturerId}}

### 3. Get classes with search
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/lecturer/classes?q=CTDL
X-User-Id: {{lecturerId}}

### 4. Get classes with term filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/lecturer/classes?termId=7ef2a9a7-cb2a-46f2-8440-fcad43230a61
X-User-Id: {{lecturerId}}

### 5. Get classes with assignment filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/lecturer/classes?assignmentId=22bfd357-e85d-40a7-8670-5bb5d545af83
X-User-Id: {{lecturerId}}